English
-------

"
&lt;p&gt;You will now see pairs of WORDS and PICTURES. Each time you have to rate if the object shown in the picture is a typical or an atypical example of the word. Use a scale from 1 (very atypical) to 7 (very typical).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Below the rating scale are two more buttons that you can use in the following situations:&lt;/p&gt;

